LANGUAGE "SIC 1.0".
SCROLL altar_inline_demo
MODE CHANT.

WORK MAIN WITH SIGIL UNUSED AS TEXT:
  SAY: "Raising ALTAR inline demo.".

  ALTAR AT :15080:
    ROUTE GET "/hello" TO SEND BACK "Hello from " + REQUEST_METHOD + " " + REQUEST_PATH + ".".
    ROUTE GET "/who"   TO SEND BACK "You are " + Q_NAME + ".".
  ENDALTAR.

ENDWORK.
